text: is a Japanese fashion model and actor. She appeared in the national "What should I do to coordinate tomorrow?" campaign for the fashion magazine ' in 2017 and 2018. While attending Kagoshima Girl's High School, she was a member of the volleyball team that went to the national finals. Obama was a finalist for the 3rd Cover Girl Prize given out by Magazine Summit, a national organization for magazine publishers in Japan. Obama has used her celebrity status to support products such as shōchū that are produced in Minamisatsuma. ==Filmography== ===Film=== *Kids (2008) *MW (2009, Kanako) ===Television=== *Nodame Cantabile (2006, guest star) *Shika Otoko A wo Niyoshi (2008, Kako Harawa) *Rinjō (2009, Sayoko Kataoka, based on the short story collection from Hideo Yokoyama) ==References== Category:1984 births Category:21st-century Japanese actresses Category:Japanese female models Category:Japanese film actresses Category:Japanese television actresses Category:Models from Kagoshima Prefecture Category:Living people
